§ 673c. Repealed. Pub. L. 109–239, § 4(c), July 3, 2006, 120 Stat. 512
Section, act Aug. 14, 1935, ch. 531, title IV, § 473B, as added Pub. L. 109–239, § 4(b), July 3, 2006, 120 Stat. 510, related to timely interstate home study incentive payments.
Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries Effective Date of RepealPub. L. 109–239, § 4(c), July 3, 2006, 120 Stat. 512, provided that the repeal of this section is effective Oct. 1, 2010.
